Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:38.01,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狐狸的单恋 爱在心头口难开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三宅家的阿忍小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是发生在何时呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6月14日 雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上又下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有事物皆宁息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承继失去梦境的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这日子 不去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想呆呆的听着温柔雨水的流动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分 那么多只欺负一只小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下没事了 小狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这是狐狸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是真不知从哪跑来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见了 小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上替你找饲主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是从哪来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住所 名字 年龄 职业呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样…我是以为狐狸会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑 开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才就一直对着地藏菩萨说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种人能保护街坊的安全吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍 要不要吃冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等再说 先到派出所去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派出所？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:06:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来想和它一起去找饲主的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 阿忍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笛恩的口红 新发售
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的嘴形非常的可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是似乎缺了点滋润
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形是很好 真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涂了口红会完全不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的运气很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在笛恩口红正优惠中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很俏丽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你皮肤白所以特别明显
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这些实话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但眼角还得装饰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魅力会完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼角装饰？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是护眼有表情的新产品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在仍是特惠期间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请算一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总共7500元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！7千！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然不够
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真想要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人送我的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有这种人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要怎么辩白呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经说要买了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是缺了点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法装笑骗过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,品质保证 现在买最合算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 7500元
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 今天我不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍 很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吵到邻居的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.33,0:00:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了 还要去补习
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想睡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.06,0:14:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才似乎有狐狸的叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻觉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿 阿忍小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是佛灭高中的老大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是来的太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这花是连老大一起甩出去的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 阿忍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 阿忍你是值日生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿当嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍 我帮你做值日生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值日生一个人太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 地板脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不弄干净会被老师骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 还很脏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍一个人一定很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 去叫老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个奇怪的诸星…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师您早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.34,0:17:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.99,0:17:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“老师您早”这优美的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能从诸星口中说出呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不是这问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning every body
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 我已经变好了才是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去不是阿当的事快暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 早
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有人知道我的眼镜在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长您来得正是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一个这个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起 诸星了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上课前擦地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不做的工作却自己做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是老师您的教导有方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位为诸星拍手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要想帮阿忍而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.53,0:18:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像诸星做了什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 达令真了不得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星！你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.46,0:19:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿当
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.74,0:19:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍是吧 我是阿当吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 阿忍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假扮的真差
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 谁是假的 一目了然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现出真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何方妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我从这学校消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的诸星同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:19:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后和老师一起求学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师最喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍 分开点比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.56,0:20:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子是妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 阿忍 危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我现出真面目 这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来想骗阿忍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何要护那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.27,0:21:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他用了我达令的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想报答昨天的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.58,0:21:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 我非常了解 回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:21:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是来报恩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:22:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人感动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活在这浊世的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.28,0:22:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什么热腾腾的东西涌起了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.06,0:22:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始上课
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.63,0:22:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚意我是很感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.45,0:22:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静 安静
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿忍真是安静的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.42,0:22:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会老师给你礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.96,0:22:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我说我是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口 你这冒牌货
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 放手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们以为我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.18,0:22:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 妖怪很吵 可以去除吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？可以去除吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是同伙 同伙的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.62,0:22:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会我可要修理你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.32,0:23:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温柔雨点的湿润
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.09,0:23:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎能比以前更喜爱的六月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.33,0:00:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========预告===========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.18,0:23:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孟夏达令们造访的乡愁世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.13,0:23:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夏日艳阳的错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.97,0:24:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁便当盒以及锡制金鱼都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.24,0:24:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介茫然 疼爱孩子之岩石之母
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.33,0:00:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========OP===========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.38,0:00:17.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连在梦中我都想追着你跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:22.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在床底放了你的相片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:32.44,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明梦见自己轻飘飘的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:39.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却在就要接吻时醒了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:48.67,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要紧紧抱住我喔 我一定会乖乖地等着的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:59.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人迫不及待 碍事的睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.67,0:01:03.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不着又觉得好难过 达令
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:11.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事的睡衣 请感受我赤裸裸的心情 达令
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:23.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叹了一口气 彷佛要燃烧起来的蓝色星球之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.33,0:00:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========ED===========
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.11,0:24:34.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要见了你 PESAMETEKIERO 在星空中踏步 AMEUSUTE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.62,0:24:46.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在银河的某处有你和我 MOBIUS的相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.22,0:24:57.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TEKIEROKISASU TEKIEROKISASU 痛苦时 PESAMERUTYO
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.40,0:25:09.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本是已约定好 PESAMERUTYO 即使等呆了 AMEUSUTE
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.88,0:25:20.43,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论距离多远的星球 以MOBIUS之环相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.48,0:25:30.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TEKIEROKISASU TEKIEROKISASU 决定好了后 PESAMERUTYO

